      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The exterior has seen some better days, with visible paint fading on the roof and trunk, along with various small scratches and a minor dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few stains on the floor mats. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a routine service in the next few thousand miles. It\u2019s an honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
